{"type":"answer","id":16528,"parentType":"question","parentId":3355,"uid":216,"contents":"有一段时间，非常喜欢满版蕾丝的连身裙，衣橱有各种正白、鹅白、粉白，大致上如下图（来源网路）<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/M25pEaG.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/M25pEaG.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/M25pEaG.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n直到某一天突然惊觉原来我在穿蚊帐。<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/IM6kmLc.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/IM6kmLc.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/IM6kmLc.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n令人后悔的衣服，还有一件浅蓝色连身裙，根本就是Cinderella（灰姑娘）本人。<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/DfdDf9E.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/DfdDf9E.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/DfdDf9E.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n穿上去是不是要十二点前回家了～（嚼嚼<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/Qi0F4Au.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Qi0F4Au.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/Qi0F4Au.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n此外，还有一些谜之流行的跟风产物。譬如泰迪熊外套、千鸟纹上衣、超长版风衣、毛毛穆勒鞋。<br>\n<br>\n有一些东西，显然不属于我。所以现在他们都在我的衣柜裡躺得很好。<br>\n<br>\n学到的道理如下图所示：<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/AkeDoKp.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/AkeDoKp.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/AkeDoKp.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2019-04-09","agreeCount":5,"discussionCount":5}